ios verdes y las circunstancias en torno al fallecimiento ocurrido el 10/12/2012. Seguidamente practicó liquidación conforme la ley 26.773, ofreció prueba y fundó en derecho, cerrando su presentación con el petitorio de estilo. II. Ordenado el traslado que mandaba el artículo 28 de la ley 11.653, el 02/07/2015 compareció a estar a derecho el demandado Pr...","embedding":[0.10030809044837952,0.024973414838314056,-0.06221315637230873,0.10460903495550156,-0.08353918045759201,0.06862571090459824,0.07559435069561005,-0.015086251311004162,-0.04692639410495758,0.0202987939119339,0.07641333341598511,-0.05068139359354973,-0.06579151749610901,-0.03908205404877663,-0.03580479696393013,0.041662998497486115,0.05198846384882927,-0.0316152460873127,-0.04381231218576431,0.013795983977615833,-0.03692413866519928,-0.013411381281912327,-0.10183949023485184,-0.015161516144871712,-0.001999404514208436,0.008859465830028057,0.0021092109382152557,0.032924629747867584,-0.016909917816519737,-0.0011540449922904372,-0.030906591564416885,-0.07750723510980606,0.003998963162302971,0.1283266246318817,0.018482066690921783,-0.09997193515300751,0.02925632707774639,0.025704652070999146,0.03848567232489586,0.0015048075001686811,-0.029617592692375183,0.060182809829711914,-0.06237097457051277,0.007846447639167309,0.004748733714222908,-0.1008891612291336,0.007562077604234219,-0.02493583969771862,-0.0649477019906044,-0.01129961758852005,-0.12178906053304672,0.01633581332862377,-0.015273197554051876,-0.0257492084056139,-0.0586635023355484,-0.05832422152161598,0.028736451640725136,0.08824210613965988,0.03148139640688896,-0.04407103732228279,0.06833738833665848,0.030105052515864372,-0.019363122060894966,-0.09138187021017075,-0.02464253269135952,-0.15580785274505615,0.03809044882655144,-0.0052797612734138966,0.04264429956674576,-0.05905161798000336,-0.005713197402656078,0.05444633215665817,-0.005254198797047138,-0.0728289857506752,-0.02249429188668728,0.022873032838106155,0.03154521435499191,0.0666011497378349